data.description: One of the largest lots in Ponderosa Cascade, this property occupies 1.44 acres. Adjacent to public land and backing onto a common area, it offers the perfect blend of seclusion & accessibility. Inside, the main living area features Hickory Hardwood Floors, while the kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, including a Dacor 6-burner Range/Double Oven with hood, tile counters &  full backsplash.There are Two Primary Suites, one on the main floor & another on the upper level. The upper-level primary suite boasts a spacious bathroom with a jetted tub & tile shower, a walk-in closet, and an adjoining room currently serving as an art studio but versatile enough to be used as an office or nursery.Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the extensive outdoor living options, including a large covered patio, back deck, and a fire pit area. Additionally, there's a detached studio measuring 14' x 28' with a covered front porch. Located in the desirable Sisters School District.
